dsDescriptionValue.value: contains average dekadal PET for 37 dekads for Cagayan province. PET was calculated using Hargreaves (1985) using mean Air Temperature (acquired thru NASA for 10 years (2003-2012)) and Extra-terrestrial radiation (computed using Allen (1998) method) as input. The file naming convention is: Cag_PET<dekad number (001-037>.<file extension>
